To move the cursor in a TextField widget in Flutter by single characters, you can create a custom `EditableText` and use this custom widget instead of the standard `TextField` widget. This custom `EditableText` widget can then implement the behavior you need to move the cursor one character to the left or right.

Here's an example of how you can create a custom `EditableText` widget and use it in place of the standard `TextField`:

```dart
class CustomEditableText extends EditableText {
  CustomEditableText({
    Key key,
